ICYCLAIR, Inc., a Corporation, et al., Appellants, v. NATIONAL POPSICLE CORPORATION, a Corporation, et al., Appellees. No. 6752. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Feb. 15, 1932.

*1080■ Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellees, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellants to file record and docket cause; mandate forthwith.
